picty (0.3a1) lucid; urgency=low

  * collections now display as "tabs"
  * the right most tab is a collection management tab displaying the list of available collections/devices
  * the management tab offers a right click context menu (open, close, delete, properties). 
  * add ability to change collection properties (and fix various collection related bugs that arose from the recent changes)
  * new browser OSD buttons: "close" and "locate in browser"
  * rotate plugin: 
    * draw gridlines over the image 
    * bug fix: image does not redraw if angle is set to zero
    * reset angle after use
  * crop plugin:
    * render background red 
    * draggable handles of the crop area
  * other bug fixes: 
    * tag pane and browser OSD text renders tags with ampersands correctly (must be escaped for pango to render correctly)
  * based on rev440 of lp:picty

 -- damien <damienlmoore@gmail.com>  Mon, 17 May 2010 21:35:50 -0400

